{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_robrta_set_1", "eventName": "輓歌", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "輓歌", "storyInfo": "在哥倫比亞，羅比菈塔為一位不幸故去的友人料理喪事。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_Morgue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這裡了，羅比菈塔女士，請節哀。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我再看看她，可以嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她看起來很平靜，沒有受太多折磨。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的病症到了末期，堅持治療已經沒有什麼意義，醫生給出的方案多是為了減輕病痛，所以......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給她用了很多鎮靜劑。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（抹掉眼角的淚水）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 4.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前，她信裡說過自己生病了，我本想迅速趕來探視，但工作緊急，我沒能抽開身。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我請好假，趕到醫院時，病床已經空了，護士聽完我的詢問就給了我這裡的地址。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸虧您今天找來了......要是再晚來一天，估計連這最後一面都見不到了，按照日程表，逝者晚上就要火化了。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來，我來得也算是及時了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對、對不起，我不是那個意思......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我沒有責怪你的意思，只是有些感歎罷了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還好嗎？如果需要的話，我可以為您拿把椅子。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了......她有留下什麼嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我們在她租住的公寓裡發現了很多化妝品，還有膠水、黏土、油彩、假髮和一些看起來非常可怕的道具陳設。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜那個房間看起來一定很像殺人魔的老巢。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們從那個房間清理出來了六罐假血漿......更別提那些假肢和假眼球了。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有其他的嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，還有她死前抱著的一本筆記。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以給我看看嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您稍等，我去拿給您。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給您，實話說，作為一個在停屍間工作的人，我完全有資格打包票，這是我這輩子見過最可怕的東西。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（翻閱）......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒想到她還留著我的照片啊。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面這個驚恐的老太太......是您嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我們當時經常拿對方練手，背後那個滿身膿包的怪物就是她。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？那是一封信嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“貝克親啟”。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "<i>羅比菈塔·貝克：</i>", "x": 200.0, "y": 220.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "<i>你這傢伙，距離上次給你寄錄影帶已經有一段時間了，你看或者沒看都給我回封信嘛。《拓荒地的活死人》這部片子票房砸了，我和馬里奧早就預想到了。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 290.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "<i>畢竟工期緊，手頭緊，做到後期頭皮也發緊，唯一不緊的是我和馬里奧因為餓肚皮而日益寬鬆的褲腰帶。馬里奧打算繼續籌拍他的下一部作品，但大佬們多多少少都聽過他的臭名聲，不願意投錢給他。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 290.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "<i>本來我是想出院做些什麼幫幫忙，但醫生面色凝重，非要我繼續留在這裡。醫院裡的日子很無聊，百無聊賴之際，我突然想起很多舊日的時光。那間我們一起擠過的地下室，那些冒著白沫的冰啤酒，那些我們百看不厭的電影......</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 290.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "<i>我真的很害怕，害怕會一個人死去，如果你能抽出時間的話，可以來看看我嗎？</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 290.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "text": "<i>我真的很想你。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 380.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "<i>辛西婭·伊蒂絲</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 430.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "stickerclear", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的很抱歉，是我們工作的疏忽，沒有發現這封信。要是當時看到它，一定第一時間聯繫您。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，這上面畫的東西確實很可怕，要你們細細翻著看純屬是難為你們，我能理解。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，都是我們的失職。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，就算你們聯繫到了我，又能怎麼樣呢？只是消息知道得早一點而已......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......人死不能復生，羅比菈塔小姐，無論如何你都來了，逝者火化前的最後一程也能有人送送了。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要做什麼嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用您做什麼，我昨天已經把她的身體清潔乾淨了，她身上的病號服也換成了常服。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩你了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該的。一會我再給她簡單地上個妝，看著能好看很多。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上妝？還有這個步驟嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，其實就是隨便描兩筆，沒有什麼技術可言的。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以......讓我來嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......不太好吧？您這樣的身份......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不忌諱這些，身上還帶了工具，正好。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就讓我像從前一樣，再為她化一次妝吧。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，也是，您肯定比我化得好。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會？在入殮這件事上，你才是專家，我一會兒肯定有需要向你請教的地方。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡哪裡......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（擦拭死者的面龐）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "ypos": 4.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道......她的死亡原因是什麼嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢性中毒，醫生判斷是長期接觸廉價劣質的顏料導致的，收拾遺物的員工也抱怨說，那些東西的味道非常刺鼻。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好像並不驚訝。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小成本製作好不容易有了資金，多請幾個身材火爆的女演員不好嗎，誰會想著花到化妝師身上呢？經費自然是一省再省。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明早就提醒過她了......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（仰頭眨眨眼睛）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，再說這些有什麼用呢？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉起刷子）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您怎麼突然停下了？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒給死去的人化過妝。她躺在我面前，卻一句話也不能和我說，我實在不知道，以什麼樣子離開才是她想要的。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，我們給逝者本人上妝，也不全是為了逝者自身的體面，有時候，我們也會按親屬希望的樣子來為逝者上妝。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您希望逝者是什麼樣，就化成什麼樣吧。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望的樣子......？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，她留在您記憶裡，最美好的樣子。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她最美好的樣子......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bar_1", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，貝克！貝克！你在想什麼呢？", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛西婭，我足足等了你一個小時你知道嗎！", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起啦，這頓我請好了。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這傢伙去哪裡了？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在街角遇到了馬里奧，和他聊了好半天，那傢伙不知道又從哪個冤大頭那裡騙來了投資，打算開始下一部片子的拍攝了。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來他還是不死心。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你猜怎麼著，我也不死心！", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，但你們之前那幾次合作實在是......不太賣座，那些鼻子放在頭頂上的影評人怎麼叫他來著，“票房毒藥”“藍卡塢的毒瘤”。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，同樣是這批人，在十五年前管他叫“血漿片之父”“恐怖片大師”。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛西婭，我們都不得不承認，現在恐怖血漿片沒有之前那麼受歡迎了，馬里奧的時代已經過去了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得嗎？那時我們擠在地下室裡一起看《嗜血保險櫃》，是那部電影啟發我們走上了電影妝造的道路。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些離奇可怕卻又逼真的形象可把我們嚇了個半死，後來，我們才知道那只是乳膠和油彩的奇跡之作。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回家路上一直喋喋不休自己有多麼震撼，我都快煩死了。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還好意思說我，明明是你自己被震驚到說不出來話，所以一路上都沒搭理我。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈哈哈哈哈。", "name": "高瘦的女人&羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......咳咳......", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（迅速遞上一杯水）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還好嗎，辛西婭？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咕咚咕咚......沒事沒事。對了，你今天約我出來是為了什麼事情，貝克？", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個歷史片的劇組找上了我，需要妝造師完成一整套維多利亞貴族女性的妝容，我想推薦你去。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的歷史片啊......你是說那些精緻的眉毛和一絲不亂的髮型嗎，“挺有意思”。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這部片子有維多利亞官方注資，經費充足，從導演到演員都是業內的佼佼者，薪水不錯還是其次，最重要的是人脈。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#9$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你，你去了肯定可以得到他們的賞識，有了這一部的合作，何愁沒有下一部。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#10$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧......算了，我已經答應馬里奧了。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛西婭，推了馬里奧的邀約吧，這是更好的機會。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝克，你說我惡趣味也好，重口味也好，但我就是對著那些血淋淋的場景才有靈感。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道你這話聽起來像個殺人魔嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好想法，聽起來是個不錯的出路。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒在開玩笑，辛西婭，你總得考慮自己的未來。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝克，我知道我參與制作的那些低成本小片子，它們情節離譜，漏洞百出，拍攝手法粗糙簡陋，千奇百怪，它們被觀眾無視，被影評人鄙視。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不在乎。在我的眼裡，它們都炫酷極了！那些主流商業大片不敢做的，它們敢做；那些流水線工業電影不敢想的，它們敢想。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們的另類、怪異、荒唐和誇張對我來說代表著自由和不受拘束，而那正是我一直以來都夢寐以求的東西。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可是兩手空空，我們要如何逐夢？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝克，人這一生真的很短暫，想要的越多反而得到的越少。有些時候，人得拋棄些有的沒的，專注於真正想要的東西。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，貝克，你真的喜歡那些作品嗎？那些所謂的符合“高雅品味”的造型，它們真的值得你傾注自己的精力和心血嗎？", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......不知道，那些作品對我來說只是工作，盡職完成就好了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你愛的呢？它們被你擱置到哪裡去了？", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等到時機成熟的時候，我、我會重拾它們的。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_524_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我等不及，我等不及！", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕不停下，絕不妥協，我要在我活著的每一天裡做我最喜愛的事，哪怕它只會讓我痛苦。", "name": "高瘦的女人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_Morgue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是有想法了嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想起了某天她對我說的話，要做自己喜歡的事情。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天是個陰天，摳門的餐館老闆還不願多開兩盞燈，室內一片昏暗，我應該看不清的......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她當時的笑臉在我的記憶中卻是那麼清晰，那麼鮮明。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前紙一樣慘白的面孔與回憶中那張充滿堅定和希望的面孔重疊，羅比菈塔舉起刷子，在屍體的面部開始塗抹起來。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨著粉底在她的刷下被一筆筆鋪開，那張死氣沉沉的面容又有了血色，乾癟的兩頰也再度飽滿起來。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（放下刷子）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您化好了嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，結束了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看起來就像是睡著了，您真的很厲害。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛入行的時候，就認識她了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我口袋裡沒有一分錢，找不到房子住，是她收留我住進了她的小地下室。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這之後，我和她一起在各個劇組間輾轉，尋找可以糊口的工作。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是個優秀的化妝師，技術精湛，可以讓一張面孔徹底成為另一張截然不同的面孔。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來，她在藍卡塢應該能賺個盆滿缽滿。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡賺錢需要的遠不止天分，她的運氣有點壞，人還非常固執，總是和機會失之交臂。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "七年，我們認識有七年了。我見過她初來此地時的意氣風發，徹夜創作時的掙扎糾結，初獲成就時的暢快淋漓，和如今......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躺在停屍間的樣子。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰冷、蒼白、死氣沉沉。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可剛剛經過您的一番修飾，她看起來好多了不是嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，可這不是我要的......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呃，這還不夠好嗎？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說......如果我真的做得足夠好......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼她的眼睛不睜開，為什麼她的心臟不跳動，為什麼她的嘴唇緊抿著......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼她只是躺在這裡......不言不語？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......因為她去世了啊。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對啊，她死了......她死了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迷茫在羅比菈塔的臉上擴散開來，她不知所措地看向那具高瘦的屍體。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痛苦抓住了機會，在她降下心防時狠狠地襲擊了她，尖銳的痛覺迅速從心臟處蔓延到她身體的每一處。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，她再難站立，蹲下身將自己蜷縮成小小一團，把臉埋在彎曲的膝蓋裡，抑制不住地悲泣出聲。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果......我能再堅決一點，強硬一點的話，是不是她就不會走到這一步？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......為什麼這麼說？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍卡塢這地方，大公司想要的，排在第一位的是聽話，第二位的是技術，理想與喜好無足輕重。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明明比誰都明白，可我當時沒有堅持說服她，我沒能那麼做......", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我......內心也曾有個聲音在發話，覺得她說的沒錯。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我選擇無視內心的呐喊，我做不到像她那樣堅持。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一路走到今天，為了填飽肚皮，我低頭了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了作品的商業價值，我放棄了很多，割捨了很多，所以我的工作變得越來越順利。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時，它們也變得越來越乏味了。我有預感，遲早有一天，我會被這些工作徹底掏空。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她初入行業時的激情與喜悅，卻從未改變過。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想，憑藉這個，說不定真的能在未來有一片獨屬於她的天地。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我心存僥倖，我以為她會是例外，我希望她會是例外......可我錯了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起......對不起，辛西婭。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅比菈塔小姐，這......怎麼會是您的錯誤？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（放聲大哭）", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，我剛剛失態了。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這有什麼，我在這裡見過很多人崩潰的樣子，您已經是非常克制的了。", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實......在你剛剛把她送進爐膛的那一瞬間，我有想過，擦乾淨她臉上的妝容。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我怎麼能用一張安詳的睡顏去詮釋她的一生呢？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把她生前經歷的一切用妝容掩蓋，強行讓她露出一副安寧的面容......這和我摒棄的那些東西有什麼區別？", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_523_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可您沒有那麼做......為什麼？", "name": "停屍間員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一刻......我突然不想做化妝師了，我告訴自己，就短短一會兒，做個敬業的入殮師吧。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓她快樂地離開，假的也好。", "name": "羅比菈塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_484_robrta_1#6$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}